frontmatter.description: Now, many have struggled to start dieting and doing exercise before me, and many will struggle after me. This post describes my story and my approach to begin exercise. It's the story of how someone who has not exercised in the last 5 years, and is not really eager to do it, will try to succeed at it.
frontmatter.title: Surviving gym
